Body:
I'm trying the Iot server 3.3.0 on windows 10 x64. After install, the broker and iot server started smoothly, but analytics starts and in few seconds crashes with errors below. I tried fire alarm sample, but cannot get any data. Using jDK 8u191, snappy java 1.1.1.7.

Please help, I don't know where to dig.
